-- China Ming Yang, Reliance in Joint Venture to Develop India Wind
-- B y   E h r e n   G o o s s e n s
-- 2012-07-02T22:12:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-02/china-ming-yang-reliance-in-joint-venture-to-develop-india-wind.html
China Ming Yang Wind Power Group
Ltd. (MY) , China’s third-largest wind-turbine manufacturer, formed a
joint venture with India’s Reliance Group to develop 2.5
gigawatts of wind farms in South Asia.  Ming Yang will provide engineering, procurement and
construction and Reliance will have a supporting role in
developing wind projects, the Zhongshan, China-based company
said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ehren Goossens in New York at 
 egoossens1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Wade at 
